title: Jamal Ahsan wins NA-89 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate, Muhammad Jamal Ahsan Khan has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-89, Mianwali-I by securing 217,427 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz candidate, Obaid Ullah Khan, who bagged 34,068 votes.
The votersâ€™ turn-out remained 54.49 %.
